From: Alistair Popple <alistair@popple.id.au>
Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/iommu: Add it_page_shift field to determine iommu page size
Git-commit: 3a553170d35d69bea3877bffa508489dfa6f133d
Patch-mainline: v3.14-rc1
References: bnc#878240,FATE#315784 

This patch adds a it_page_shift field to struct iommu_table and
initiliases it to 4K for all platforms.

Signed-off-by: Alistair Popple <alistair@popple.id.au>
Signed-off-by: Benjamin Herrenschmidt <benh@kernel.crashing.org>
Acked-by: Torsten Duwe <duwe@suse.de>

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/include/asm/iommu.h b/arch/powerpc/include/asm/iommu.h
